node.text:
#DonaldTrump says he would hop in the ring with #JoeBiden. According to TMZ, #45 faced the media at the Evander Holyfield vs. Vitor Belfort presser before his big commentary gig for Saturday's event ... when he was asked who he'd want to face off against in the ring for a hypothetical fight.

"If you said if I had to box somebody, I think probably my easiest fight would be Joe Biden," Trump said. "Because I think he'd go down very, very quickly. Very, very quickly." What y’all think about this⁉️

node.text: #Apple’s #iPhone14 has been leaked‼️🤯 This leak comes before the #iPhone13 even had the chance to be released. The rumors state that the 14 will be slightly thicker, but it will feature round buttons, a titanium chassis, camera’s incorporated into the glass, and new speakers. After hearing this, are y’all going to wait for the 14 instead⁉️🤔 FOLLOW @steez FOR MORE‼️➡️
